text: Amazing church and amazing people. We have been there, wonderful hospitality. I highly recommend the church for people around this area and new comers to Singapore. Love it
Small homely church in Geylang with a welcoming bunch of people. Service starts at 9am weekly on Sunday and 5pm on the last Sunday of the month.
A welcoming and cozy non-denominational family church - been attending for the past 5 years and grown a lot in faith and maturity as a person
wow! great church :) drummer is quite cool
